

## Differences to the Berlin theme

### show.php

- put the Viewer on top of the page
- use a custom citation style as defined in custom.php, using
  DC:BibliographicCitation


### browse.php

- do not show images of the files (mostly boring journal print in black and
  white, nothing to see really)
- show the date of the item


# sass

- changed base width in skeleton.scss from 960 to 1020px
- changed $base-font-size to a slightly bigger value
- changed $base-line-height to 18px (a bigger value)
- changed all html headings to smaller values
- changed *browse-item* settings
	- inserted new class for date
	- removed column restriction for the title (commented out)
